---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import InfoPageLayout from '../../layouts/InfoPageLayout.astro'

import contentImage from '../../assets/commercial-roof.jpg';
---

<BaseLayout>
  <InfoPageLayout>
    <Fragment slot="pageTag">Secure Your Business with Professional Roofing</Fragment>
    <Fragment slot="pageDetails">
      A well-maintained roof is crucial to the safety, comfort, and operational efficiency of 
      your building. Over time, roofs can deteriorate from wear and tear, weather conditions, 
      and lack of proper upkeep, leading to potential disruptions to your business. We understand that your 
      property needs a roof that is reliable and built to last. Whether you're looking to install 
      a brand-new roof, need a timely repair, or require ongoing maintenance, we have the expertise and tools to meet your needs.
    </Fragment>
    <img slot="heroImage" src={contentImage.src} alt="Windows and doors" />
  </InfoPageLayout>
</BaseLayout>
